Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP14.core.messages.updates

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UIUpdateMessage
    Message sent from the server to update the UI of the clients.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BuildPhaseMessage
    Message that tells the client that the build phase of a certain player has started.
    DomeBuildMessage
    Message that tells the client that a dome has been built.
    GodUpdateMessage
    Message that tells the client that a player has chosen a certain god.
    MovePhaseMessage
    Message that tells the client that a player move phase has started.
    PhaseMessage
    Blueprint for a message that tells the client that a phase has started.
    PlayerRegisterMessage
    Message that tells the client to register a new player.
    TowerIncrementMessage
    Message that tells the client that a tower size has been increased.
    UnregisterPlayerMessage
    Message that tells the client to unregister a player from the match.
    WorkerAddMessage
    Message that tells the client that a new worker has been added to the match.
    WorkerChoicePhaseMessage
    Message that tells the client that a player is choosing which worker to move.
    WorkerMoveMessage
    Message that tells the client that a player is choosing where to move a worker.
    WorkerPlacementPhaseMessage
    Message that tells the client that a player is choosing where to place their workers.
